## 1. Create the Solution
**Action**: Open your terminal and run these exact commands:
```bash
# 1. Install the Avalonia templates if you haven't
dotnet new install Avalonia.Templates

# 2. Create the main project
dotnet new avalonia.app -o HealthCenter.Desktop

# 3. Create the Solution file
cd HealthCenter.Desktop
dotnet new sln -n HealthCenter

# 4. Add the project to the solution
dotnet sln add HealthCenter.Desktop.csproj
```

## 2. Install Packages
**Action**: Install the necessary dependencies for the team:
```bash
# ReactiveUI for MVVM
dotnet add package Avalonia.ReactiveUI

# EntityFramework for Database
dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite
dotnet add package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Design

# Logging
dotnet add package Serilog
dotnet add package Serilog.Sinks.File
```

